        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Why People's Zone?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">We connect communities with powerful tools to raise funds for local causes, health needs, education, and more.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-xl transition">
