            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Create Campaigns</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Easily set up campaigns with images, goals, and stories that inspire action.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-xl transition">
            <div class="text-yellow-500 text-4xl mb-4">🤝</div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Build Communities</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Bring people together around causes that matter most to them.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-xl transition">
